'''約翰·戴維·邁克菲'''（{{lang-en|John David McAfee}}<ref>{{cite web |title=FEC FORM 2 |url=http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/254/201509089001618254/201509089001618254.pdf |publisher=Federal Election Commission |accessdate=2015-09-09 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227094743/http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/254/201509089001618254/201509089001618254.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>；{{bd|1945年|9月18日|2021年|6月23日|catIdx=McAfee}}）<ref name="fec2015">{{cite web |title=FEC Form 2 |url=http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/254/201509089001618254/201509089001618254.pdf |publisher=Federal Election Commission |accessdate=2015-09-09 |quote=John David McAfee. Office Sought: Presidential |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227094743/http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/254/201509089001618254/201509089001618254.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://link.brightcove.com/services/player/bcpid65694806001?bctid=45365945001&iframe=true&width=700&height=410 | title=Quick Tips: How Do You Pronounce McAfee | first=Scott | last=Taschler | publisher=McAfee, Inc. | date=2010-09-01 | access-date=2020-10-07 | archive-date=2021-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307200026/http://link.brightcove.com/services/player/bcpid65694806001?bctid=45365945001&iframe=true&width=700&height=410 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，英裔美國[[程序員|程式設計師]]、商人和政治家。1987年创办[[迈克菲|迈克菲]]公司，经营至1994年从公司离职。曾参选[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]{{le|2016年自由意志黨總統提名初選|Libertarian Party presidential primaries, 2016|自由意志黨的總統提名}}，但最後敗給前{{le|新墨西哥州州長|Governor of New Mexico}}[[加里·約翰遜|加里·約翰遜]]。

==生平==
約翰·邁克菲是第一個商業化[[杀毒软件|防毒軟體]][[Intel_Security|邁克菲]]的開發者，經營多年後賣給[[英特尔|英特尔]]並冠上其品牌名稱。在其投資遭受[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|2007年的全球金融危機]]前，最頂峰時他的財產價值多過1億美元。

离开迈克菲公司后，他创立了Tribal Voice（制作PowWow聊天软件）、QuorumEx和Future Tense Central等公司，并曾在Everykey、MGT Capital Investments、Luxcore等公司担任领导职务。其个人和商业取向包括智能手机应用、[[加密货币|加密货币]]、[[瑜伽|瑜伽]]<ref name="SiliconAngle1">{{cite web |url=http://siliconangle.com/blog/2014/02/11/john-mcafee-has-had-enough-of-excessive-app-permissions-introduces-cognizant/ |title=John McAfee has had enough of excessive app permissions – introduces Cognizant |publisher=[[SiliconAngle|SiliconAngle]] |date=2014-02-11 |accessdate=2014-02-11 |first=John |last=Casaretto |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222003053/http://siliconangle.com/blog/2014/02/11/john-mcafee-has-had-enough-of-excessive-app-permissions-introduces-cognizant/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和天然[[抗细菌药|抗细菌药]]<ref name="fast-company">{{cite web|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/node/1615167/print|title=Plagued by Lawsuits, McAfee Founder Hunts for Cures in Belize|publisher=Fast Company|format=article|date=2010-05-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424054349/http://www.fastcompany.com/node/1615167/print|archivedate=2010年4月24日}}</ref><ref name="gizmodo1">{{cite web |url=http://gizmodo.com/5958877 |title=Secrets, Schemes, and Lots of Guns: Inside John McAfee’s Heart of Darkness |first=Jeff |last=Wise |publisher=[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] |date=2012-11-08 |access-date=2016-08-11 |archive-date=2013-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130115231510/http://gizmodo.com/5958877 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曾在[[伯利茲|伯利茲]]居住多年，但經過和伯利茲及[[危地馬拉|危地馬拉]]政府當局的糾紛後<ref>{{cite news|last=Zarrella|first=John|title=John McAfee says he faked heart attack to avoid deportation to Belize|url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/12/13/justice/florida-john-mcafee/index.html?hpt=hp_t4|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2012-12-14|archive-date=2012-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121217055611/http://www.cnn.com/2012/12/13/justice/florida-john-mcafee/index.html?hpt=hp_t4|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他在2013年回到美國[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]][[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Software Millionaire John McAfee Says He Is Now Calling Portland Home |first=Mary Emily |last=O'Hara |work=Willamette Week |date=2013-01-11 |url=http://www.wweek.com/portland/blog-29632-software_millionaire_john_mcafee_says_he_is_now_calling_portland_home.html |accessdate=2013-02-23 |archive-date=2013-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130211090947/http://www.wweek.com/portland/blog-29632-software_millionaire_john_mcafee_says_he_is_now_calling_portland_home.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

